<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
		<link href="/admin/config.yml" type="text/yaml" rel="cms-config-url" />
		<title>لوحة المحتوى / Content Manager</title>
		<style>
			:root {
				color-scheme: light;
				font-family: "Roboto", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
				background: #f5f7fb;
				color: #111827;
			}

			body {
				margin: 0;
				min-height: 100vh;
				background:
					radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(18, 100, 163, 0.12), transparent 28%),
					linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #eef2ff 100%);
			}

			.noscript {
				max-width: 36rem;
				margin: 12vh auto 0;
				padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 1rem;
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
				box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
				line-height: 1.7;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<noscript>
			<div class="noscript">
				JavaScript is required to load the CMS. Enable JavaScript and reload this page.<br />
				يلزم تفعيل JavaScript لفتح لوحة المحتوى. فعّل JavaScript ثم أعد تحميل الصفحة.
			</div>
		</noscript>
		<script src="https://unpkg.com/decap-cms@^3.1.2/dist/decap-cms.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>